---

---

<html lang="fr">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
		<title>Clinitex × Kokoro — Journée Comptabilité (2 juin)</title>
		<meta name="description" content="Service Comptabilité — 2 juin 2026." />
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
		<script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@0.460.0/dist/umd/lucide.min.js" defer></script>
		<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3.12.5/dist/gsap.min.js" defer></script>
		<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gsap@3.12.5/dist/ScrollTrigger.min.js" defer></script>
	</head>
	<body>

		<section class="hero" id="hero">
			<div class="hero-glow"></div>
			<div class="container">
				<div class="cover-logos">
					<span class="cover-logo">Clinitex</span>
					<span class="cover-x">&times;</span>
					<span class="cover-logo">Kokoro</span>
				</div>
				<p class="hero-eyebrow">Journée Comptabilité</p>
				<h1>Rentabilité &amp; recouvrement.<br/>Sur <span class="gradient-text">vos vraies données</span>.</h1>
				<div class="cover-meta">
					<span><i data-lucide="calendar" style="width:14px;height:14px;vertical-align:-2px;margin-right:4px;"></i> 2 juin 2026</span>
					<span><i data-lucide="clock" style="width:14px;height:14px;vertical-align:-2px;margin-right:4px;"></i> 9h &ndash; 17h</span>
					<span><i data-lucide="users" style="width:14px;height:14px;vertical-align:-2px;margin-right:4px;"></i> 9 personnes</span>
					<span><i data-lucide="map-pin" style="width:14px;height:14px;vertical-align:-2px;margin-right:4px;"></i> Villeneuve d'Ascq</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section" id="remontee">
			<div class="container">
				<p class="section-label reveal">Ce qui remonte</p>
				<h2 class="reveal">Le contexte</h2>
				<p class="section-sub reveal">Pas encore de retour formulaire côté Compta — <strong>à relancer</strong>. Voici ce qu'on sait du call du 9 avril.</p>
				<div class="cards-grid cards-3 reveal-group">
					<div class="card reveal">
						<div class="card-icon"><i data-lucide="trending-up"></i></div>
						<h3>Tous sur la rentabilité</h3>
						<p>7 personnes sur les sujets de rentabilité par agence.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="card reveal">
						<div class="card-icon"><i data-lucide="credit-card"></i></div>
						<h3>2 sur le recouvrement</h3>
						<p>Sous-groupe dédié aux impayés et relances.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="card reveal">
						<div class="card-icon"><i data-lucide="alert-circle"></i></div>
						<h3>Niveau IA bas</h3>
						<p>Frustration forte Metabase : 6 mois d'attente pour des chiffres fiables.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section" id="cas-usage">
			<div class="container">
				<p class="section-label reveal">Cas d'usage</p>
				<h2 class="reveal">Ce qu'on travaille le jour J</h2>
				<p class="section-sub reveal">À affiner après retour formulaire. Focus sur <strong>ce qui est faisable en Claude Pro</strong>.</p>
				<div class="acte-list">
					<div class="acte-item reveal">
						<div class="acte-icon"><i data-lucide="file-text"></i></div>
						<div>
							<h3>Analyse de factures fournisseurs</h3>
							<p>Upload PDF, extraction des données clés, détection d'anomalies, rapprochement avec les commandes.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="acte-item reveal">
						<div class="acte-icon"><i data-lucide="bar-chart-3"></i></div>
						<div>
							<h3>Rentabilité par agence</h3>
							<p>Analyse d'un export comptable, synthèse structurée, génération d'un dashboard Artifacts one-shot.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="acte-item reveal">
						<div class="acte-icon"><i data-lucide="phone-outgoing"></i></div>
						<div>
							<h3>Priorisation impayés &amp; relances</h3>
							<p>Balance clients → priorisation + génération de courriers et scripts d'appel personnalisés.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="acte-item reveal">
						<div class="acte-icon"><i data-lucide="bot"></i></div>
						<div>
							<h3>Project Claude "Compta Clinitex"</h3>
							<p>On crée ensemble un Project avec les procédures internes en knowledge. L'assistant compta quotidien de l'équipe.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<p class="note-inline reveal">Automatisations récurrentes (rapprochement bancaire auto, envoi relances) = hors scope formation. À faire via Pennylane / Cegid / n8n.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section" id="timeline">
			<div class="container">
				<p class="section-label reveal">Déroulé</p>
				<h2 class="reveal">La journée</h2>
				<div class="program-timeline">
					<div class="program-step">
						<div class="program-dot"></div>
						<div class="program-step-card">
							<div class="program-time">9h00</div>
							<h3>Ouverture &amp; socle commun</h3>
							<p>Tour de table, confidentialité des données comptables, prompting, choix de Claude.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="program-step">
						<div class="program-dot program-dot--accent"></div>
						<div class="program-step-card program-step-card--accent">
							<div class="program-time">11h00</div>
							<h3>Rentabilité sur données réelles</h3>
							<p>Analyse d'un export comptable anonymisé, synthèse par agence, dashboard one-shot.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="program-step">
						<div class="program-dot program-dot--muted"></div>
						<div class="program-step-card">
							<div class="program-time">12h30</div>
							<h3>Déjeuner</h3>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="program-step">
						<div class="program-dot program-dot--accent"></div>
						<div class="program-step-card program-step-card--accent">
							<div class="program-time">14h00</div>
							<h3>Sous-groupes</h3>
							<p>Rentabilité (7) : factures fournisseurs + clôture.<br/>Recouvrement (2) : priorisation + relances.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="program-step">
						<div class="program-dot program-dot--green"></div>
						<div class="program-step-card program-step-card--green">
							<div class="program-time">15h45</div>
							<h3>Project "Compta Clinitex"</h3>
							<p>Construction collective : knowledge, prompt système, premiers tests.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="program-step">
						<div class="program-dot"></div>
						<div class="program-step-card">
							<div class="program-time">16h45</div>
							<h3>Clôture</h3>
							<p>Feuille de route perso, 3 actions à activer la semaine suivante.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section" id="docs">
			<div class="why-claude-bg-glow"></div>
			<div class="container" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
				<p class="section-label reveal">Préparation</p>
				<h2 class="reveal">Docs à envoyer en amont</h2>
				<p class="section-sub reveal">À transmettre <strong>2 semaines avant</strong>. Et <strong>relancer le formulaire</strong> auprès de l'équipe.</p>
				<div class="check-grid reveal-group">
					<div class="check-item reveal">
						<div class="check-icon"><i data-lucide="file-text"></i></div>
						<div><h3>Export comptable anonymisé</h3><p>Balance, grand livre ou FEC.</p></div>
					</div>
					<div class="check-item reveal">
						<div class="check-icon"><i data-lucide="receipt"></i></div>
						<div><h3>3-5 factures fournisseurs types</h3><p>PDF anonymisés.</p></div>
					</div>
					<div class="check-item reveal">
						<div class="check-icon"><i data-lucide="users"></i></div>
						<div><h3>Balance clients + procédure relance</h3><p>Anonymisée, avec échéancier.</p></div>
					</div>
					<div class="check-item reveal">
						<div class="check-icon"><i data-lucide="layout-dashboard"></i></div>
						<div><h3>Tableau de bord attendu</h3><p>Celui qu'ils espèrent de Metabase.</p></div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="section closing" id="closing">
			<div class="final-glow"></div>
			<div class="container" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
				<h2 class="reveal">Rendez-vous le <span class="gradient-text">2 juin</span>.</h2>
				<p class="closing-meta reveal">Clinitex &times; Kokoro &middot; Journée Comptabilité</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<script>
			document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
				if (window.lucide) lucide.createIcons();
				if (window.gsap && window.ScrollTrigger) {
					gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);
					document.querySelectorAll('section').forEach(section => {
						const els = section.querySelectorAll('.reveal');
						if (els.length) {
							gsap.fromTo(els, { opacity: 0, y: 30, filter: 'blur(4px)' },
								{ opacity: 1, y: 0, filter: 'blur(0px)', duration: 0.8, stagger: 0.12, ease: 'power3.out',
								  scrollTrigger: { trigger: section, start: 'top 80%', once: true } });
						}
					});
					gsap.fromTo('.cover-logos', { opacity: 0, y: 20 }, { opacity: 1, y: 0, duration: 0.7, delay: 0.2, ease: 'power3.out' });
					gsap.fromTo('.hero-eyebrow', { opacity: 0, y: 20 }, { opacity: 1, y: 0, duration: 0.7, delay: 0.35, ease: 'power3.out' });
					gsap.fromTo('.hero h1', { opacity: 0, y: 30 }, { opacity: 1, y: 0, duration: 0.8, delay: 0.5, ease: 'power3.out' });
					gsap.fromTo('.cover-meta', { opacity: 0, y: 20 }, { opacity: 1, y: 0, duration: 0.7, delay: 0.7, ease: 'power3.out' });
					gsap.fromTo('.program-dot', { opacity: 0, scale: 0 },
						{ opacity: 1, scale: 1, duration: 0.4, stagger: 0.12, ease: 'back.out(2)',
						  scrollTrigger: { trigger: '.program-timeline', start: 'top 80%', once: true } });
					document.querySelectorAll('.program-step').forEach((step, i) => {
						const card = step.querySelector('.program-step-card');
						const fromX = i % 2 === 0 ? -40 : 40;
						gsap.fromTo(card, { opacity: 0, x: fromX },
							{ opacity: 1, x: 0, duration: 0.6, ease: 'power3.out',
							  scrollTrigger: { trigger: step, start: 'top 85%', once: true } });
					});
				}
			});
		</script>
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
	html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
	body { font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, system-ui, sans-serif; background: #0A0812; color: hsla(0,0%,100%,.6); line-height: 1.7; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
	.container { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 28px; }
	.reveal { opacity: 0; }
	h1, h2 { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.04em; }
	h3 { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
	.gradient-text { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4D9DE0, #0055A4, #7EC8E3); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text; }
	.section-label { font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 5px; color: #4D9DE0; font-weight: 600; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px; }
	.section-sub { font-size: 17px; color: hsla(0,0%,100%,.55); max-width: 650px; margin: -32px auto 64px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.7; }
	.section-sub strong { color: hsla(0,0%,100%,.9); }
	.section { padding: 120px 0; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
	h2 { font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 48px); font-weight: 800; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 64px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.1; }
	.hero { padding: 180px 0 120px; text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden; min-height: 90vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
	.hero .container { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
	.hero-glow { position: absolute; top: -200px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 1000px; height: 700px; background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(0,85,164,0.35) 0%, rgba(77,157,224,0.15) 35%, rgba(0,85,164,0.05) 60%, transparent 75%); pointer-events: none; animation: heroPulse 6s ease-in-out infinite; }
	@keyframes heroPulse { 0%,100% { opacity: 0.7; transform: translateX(-50%) scale(1); } 50% { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(-50%) scale(1.08); } }
	.cover-logos { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 24px; opacity: 0; }
	.cover-logo { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase; color: hsla(0,0%,100%,.9); }
	.cover-x { font-size: 16px; color: hsla(0,0%,100%,.25); font-weight: 500; }
	.hero-eyebrow { font-size: 13px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 5px; color: #4D9DE0; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 28px; opacity: 0; }
	.hero h1 { font-size: clamp(30px, 4.5vw, 48px); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 40px; opacity: 0; }
	.cover-meta { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 24px; flex-wrap: wrap; opacity: 0; }
	.cover-meta span { font-size: 13px; color: hsla(0,0%,100%,.45); font-weight: 500; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; }
	.cards-grid { display: grid; gap: 20px; }
	.cards-3 { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
	.card { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border: 1px dashed rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 16px; padding: 36px 28px; transition: all .4s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1); position: relative; }
	.card:hover { background: rgba(0,85,164,0.05); border-color: rgba(0,85,164,0.2); box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(0,85,164,0.08); }
	.card-icon { color: #4D9DE0; margin-bottom: 16px; }
	.card-icon i, .card-icon svg { width: 24px; height: 24px; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 8px rgba(0,85,164,0.4)); }
	.card h3 { font-size: 16px; color: hsla(0,0%,100%,.9); margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.4; }
	.card p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; color: hsla(0,0%,100%,.6); }
	.check-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; }
	.check-item { display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: flex-start; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px; transition: all .4s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1); }
	.check-item:hover { background: rgba(0,85,164,0.05); border-color: rgba(0,85,164,0.15); }
	.check-icon { width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; background: rgba(0,85,164,0.1); color: #4D9DE0; }
	.check-icon i, .check-icon svg { width: 20px; height: 20px; }
	.check-item h3 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: hsla(0,0%,100%,.9); margin-bottom: 4px; }
	.check-item p { font-size: 13px; color: hsla(0,0%,100%,.5); line-height: 1.5; }
	.program-timeline { position: relative; padding: 40px 0; }
	.program-timeline::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 50%; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 2px; transform: translateX(-50%); background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,85,164,0.15), rgba(0,85,164,0.5) 20%, rgba(0,85,164,0.5) 80%, rgba(0,85,164,0.15)); }
	.program-step { position: relative; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 32px; width: 100%; }
	.program-step:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
	.program-step:nth-child(odd) { justify-content: flex-start; padding-right: calc(50% + 28px); }
	.program-step:nth-child(even) { justify-content: flex-end; padding-left: calc(50% + 28px); }
	.program-dot { position: absolute; left: 50%; top: 20px; width: 14px; height: 14px; border-radius: 50%; background: #0055A4; transform: translateX(-50%); box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(0,85,164,0.5), 0 0 24px rgba(0,85,164,0.2); z-index: 2; opacity: 0; }
	.program-dot--accent { background: #4D9DE0; box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(77,157,224,0.6), 0 0 24px rgba(77,157,224,0.3); }
	.program-dot--green { background: #22C55E; box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(34,197,94,0.5), 0 0 24px rgba(34,197,94,0.2); }
	.program-dot--muted { background: hsla(0,0%,100%,.25); box-shadow: none; }
	.program-step-card { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px 22px; transition: all .4s cubic-bezier(.22,1,.36,1); width: 100%; opacity: 0; }
	.program-step-card:hover { background: rgba(0,85,164,0.05); border-color: rgba(0,85,164,0.15); }
	.program-step-card--accent { background: rgba(0,85,164,0.06); border-color: rgba(0,85,164,0.2); }
	.program-step-card--green { background: rgba(34,197,94,0.04); border-color: rgba(34,197,94,0.15); }
	.program-time { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: #4D9DE0; letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-bottom: 8px; text-transform: uppercase; }
	.program-step-card h3 { font-size: 15px; color: hsla(0,0%,100%,.85); margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 700; }
	.program-step-card p { font-size: 13px; color: hsla(0,0%,100%,.55); line-height: 1.65; margin: 0; }
	.acte-list { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
	.acte-item { display: flex; gap: 20px; padding: 26px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); align-items: flex-start; }
	.acte-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
	.acte-icon { width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; background: rgba(0,85,164,0.1); color: #4D9DE0; border: 1px solid rgba(0,85,164,0.15); }
	.acte-icon i, .acte-icon svg { width: 22px; height: 22px; }
	.acte-item h3 { font-size: 16px; color: hsla(0,0%,100%,.9); margin-bottom: 6px; }
	.acte-item p { font-size: 14px; color: hsla(0,0%,100%,.55); line-height: 1.7; margin: 0; }
	.note-inline { text-align: center; max-width: 650px; margin: 40px auto 0; font-size: 13px; color: hsla(0,0%,100%,.4); font-style: italic; }
	.why-claude-bg-glow { position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%,-50%); width: 900px; height: 600px; background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(0,85,164,0.12) 0%, rgba(77,157,224,0.05) 40%, transparent 70%); pointer-events: none; }
	.closing { text-align: center; padding: 140px 0; min-height: 80vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
	.closing h2 { margin-bottom: 28px; }
	.closing-meta { font-size: 15px; color: hsla(0,0%,100%,.3); font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 1px; }
	.final-glow { position: absolute; bottom: -100px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 800px; height: 500px; background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(0,85,164,0.1) 0%, rgba(77,157,224,0.04) 40%, transparent 70%); pointer-events: none; }
	.program-step-card { opacity: 0; }
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.hero { padding: 100px 0 60px; } .section { padding: 70px 0; }
		.hero h1 { font-size: clamp(24px, 7vw, 36px); }
		h2 { font-size: clamp(24px, 6vw, 36px); margin-bottom: 40px; }
		.section-sub { margin: -16px auto 40px; font-size: 15px; }
		.cards-3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
		.check-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
		.cover-meta { flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
		.program-timeline::before { left: 16px; }
		.program-dot { left: 16px; }
		.program-step:nth-child(odd), .program-step:nth-child(even) { padding-left: 44px; padding-right: 0; justify-content: flex-start; }
		.acte-item { gap: 14px; }
	}
</style>
</html>
